{"componentChunkName":"component---theme-src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/post/grub-rescue/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>前些天把很久没用的 Windows10 更新了下，更新后就进不了 Linux 系统了，提示 \"file '/boot/grub/x86_64-efi/normal.mod' not found\"，之后就进入 grub rescue 模式了</p>\n<p>解决方法很简单，在 grub rescue 模式下找到系统的启动分区，手动启动系统，之后重新安装 grub 到 efi 分区即可</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h3 id=\"grub-rescue-下的操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grub-rescue-%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"grub rescue 下的操作 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>grub rescue 下的操作</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 查看设备和分区情况</span>\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ls</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd0, gpt2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd0, gpt1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看分区文件确定启动分区位置</span>\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd1, gpt10<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>/\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 设置启动分区，载入启动需要的模块</span>\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">root</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd1, gpt10<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">prefix</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>hd1, gpt10<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>/boot/grub\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> insmod normal\ngrub rescue<span class=\"token operator\">></span> normal</code></pre></div>\n<p>执行完 normal 命令后，顺利的话就能进入系统了</p>\n<h3 id=\"查找-bootefi\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE-bootefi\" aria-label=\"查找 bootefi permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>查找 boot/efi</h3>\n<p>通过命令 <strong>df</strong> 查看 boot/efi 所在挂载点</p>\n<!-- {% imgurl 'grub-rescue/grub.png' alt:grub %} -->\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 572px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Raincal/gatsby-theme-rocket@web/static/ea3fe79e2c1303d896759c196d34beac/a805e/grub.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.0188679245283%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"grub\"\n        title=\"grub\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Raincal/gatsby-theme-rocket@web/static/ea3fe79e2c1303d896759c196d34beac/a805e/grub.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Raincal/gatsby-theme-rocket@web/static/ea3fe79e2c1303d896759c196d34beac/78e79/grub.png 265w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Raincal/gatsby-theme-rocket@web/static/ea3fe79e2c1303d896759c196d34beac/b6a9b/grub.png 530w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Raincal/gatsby-theme-rocket@web/static/ea3fe79e2c1303d896759c196d34beac/a805e/grub.png 572w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"重新安装-grub\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-grub\" aria-label=\"重新安装 grub permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>重新安装 grub</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">➜ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> grub-install /dev/sda1</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"前些天把很久没用的 Windows10 更新了下，更新后就进不了 Linux 系统了，提示 \"file '/boot/grub/x86_64-efi/normal.mod' not found\"，之后就进入 grub rescue 模式了 解决方法很简单，在 grub rescue…","frontmatter":{"date":"11月22, 2017","title":"grub rescue 模式下修复 Linux 引导","tags":["Linux","grub","Arch"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/grub-rescue/","prev":{"slug":"/post/vscode-icon-share/","title":"VSCode icon 分享"},"next":{"slug":"/post/hello-2018/","title":"Hello 2018"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3020019608","3128451518"]}